itunes:title: Listen to this if you're a human with feelings
title: Listen to this if you're a human with feelings
itunes:author: Joey Kidney
description:
This is for anyone going through life and not knowing if they are ready. In today's podcast, we go over a few updates in my life and talk about feeling a little lost, and why I stopped wearing a wedding ring.
